  <lyrics>[V1]
 Khespiyir Cristoru jutjjamay jilata,
 Jupaquiw Awquimajj iyawsaquimaya.
 
[C]
 Jichhüruw waquisi
 Tatitur jaysañajj;
 :Kharürojj jayp'uniw,
 Janiw utj-jjaniti. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Tatitur arsusim take juchanaca,
 Perdonasítamwa jan mayampitaqui.
 
[V3]
 Tatitur catokam Khespiyirimata.
 Wilap wartawayi jumar munasinjja.
 
[V4]
 Khespiyir Cristojja suma wawapata
 Catokañ muntamjja, maqhatam j upar u.
 
</lyrics></song>